title: LF Levelling Partner
body:
I'm about level 14 on EUW and levelling is going pretty slow, so looking for anyone to queue with to make it a bit more exciting. I don't mind whether you are a smurf or a new player.

I'm only a gold support main, so I can help anyone new with basics, but I'm not the best player - just looking to have fun :D

~~ROX Abb
